sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_046_CSMS (Table 166, Page 142/176)
    Note over CP,CS: Reservation of a Connector - Transaction
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag>
    Note left of CS: Validation (CS-SUT):<br/>connectorId should be <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag should be <Configured Valid IdTag>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req (status: Reserved)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Reserved
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over CP,CS: 5. Execute Reusable State: Charging (Table 201)<br/>Depends on Reusable State: Authorized (Table 200)

        Note over CP,CS: --- Reusable State: Authorized ---
        CP->>CS: 5a. Authorize.req (idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag>)
        CS-->>CP: 5b. Authorize.conf
        Note over CS: Validation: idTagInfo.status should be Accepted

        Note over CP,CS: --- Reusable State: Charging ---
        CP->>CS: 5c. StatusNotification.req (status: Preparing, connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId>)
        CS-->>CP: 5d. StatusNotification.conf

        CP->>CS: 5e. StartTransaction.req
        Note right of CP: idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>reservationId: from step 1
        CS-->>CP: 5f. StartTransaction.conf
        Note over CS: Validation: idTagInfo.status should be Accepted
        Note over CP: Validation: reservationId is the reservationId from step 1

        CP->>CS: 5g. StatusNotification.req (status: Charging, connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId>)
        CS-->>CP: 5h. StatusNotification.conf
    end
